snippet.textDisplay: "All this fighting, day after day, must come to an end! This land... long ago, it belonged to all of us! Now look at us. ALLIES TURNED ENEMIES! You used to be inseparable, now all you care about is {winning all of your petty battles!} Do you even know what you are fighting for anymore? ANY OF YOU? You're all so concerned about whether or not you're on the right side! Did you even consider that you shouldn't be choosing sides in the first place?! What would winning this tired feud mean at this point? NOTHING. ​​​​​​​Victory achieved through bloodshed- is a victory tainted by loss! The path of unity, of mutual respect, and ​​​​​​​compromise, is the ONLY path to everyone truly winning this war!  Please, let's go home! Go home and kiss your families, go home and pet your bony hounds- go home."
